*****************************************************************
* Programming Style - ABC chapter 8                             *
*****************************************************************

  ABC chapter 8 is concerned with programming style.
  This is divided into 3 main areas :-
                         CLARITY
                         CONCISENESS
                         EFFICIENCY
  The programs in this chapter try to illuminate the prescence  of 
  these parameters by comparing different codings which solve the 
  same problem.
  I have only included the 'C' source here as the assembler and 
  .PRG  code is not really relevant.

***************************************************************** 
